    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Pristine Mint-Condition Gem \u2013 Practically Brand New! \ud83c\udf1f\n\nThis is the real deal, folks! We are genuinely excited to present a vehicle in true mint condition \u2014 spotless inside and out, with everything functioning exactly as it should. The exterior gleams without a scratch or blemish, the interior is immaculate with zero wear, and every system runs flawlessly. This car has been exceptionally well cared for and it absolutely shows from the moment you lay eyes on it.\n\nIf you've been searching for a vehicle that feels fresh off the lot without the new-car price tag, your search ends here. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will speak for itself. Don't miss this rare opportunity! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make your decision. The exterior shows its age \u2014 expect noticeable scratches, some paint fade, and minor dents in a few areas. The interior is functional but worn, with scuffs on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard trim. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance and attention to minor wear items. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for an affordable, usable vehicle who doesn't mind cosmetic imperfections and is prepared for the typical upkeep that comes with a car at this stage of its life.",
      "price": 15000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Reliable, well-maintained, and ready to impress \u2014 this is a car you can feel confident about! This vehicle is in good condition, meaning it's been well cared for and shows only the minor signs of wear you'd expect from a pre-owned car. It drives smoothly, looks great, and is ready to take on whatever comes next. If you're looking for a dependable ride that delivers real value without the mint-condition price tag, look no further \u2014 this one checks all the boxes!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you about what you're getting. The exterior has seen significant wear \u2014 there are multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and areas where the paint has faded, chipped, or is beginning to rust. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car requires attention \u2014 it has known issues that will need to be addressed, and we strongly recommend a full inspection by a qualified mechanic before purchase. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is handy with repairs, looking for a project car, or simply needs basic transportation and is prepared for ongoing maintenance. Priced accordingly to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, making it an excellent choice for buyers seeking a reliable, well-maintained used vehicle without paying a premium for mint condition. The exterior presents nicely with only minor cosmetic imperfections \u2014 small scratches or light scuffs that come naturally with regular use \u2014 but no significant dents, rust, or damage. The interior is clean and functional, showing normal wear consistent with its age, including slight fading or minor wear on high-contact surfaces, but nothing that detracts meaningfully from comfort or usability. Mechanically, this car runs well and has been properly maintained; you can expect dependable everyday performance without looming repair concerns. It starts reliably, drives smoothly, and all major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and electronics \u2014 are in good working order. This is the kind of car you can buy with confidence and drive immediately without hesitation.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
